official_title: To repeal the annual fee on health insurance providers enacted by the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act.

summary.text: Amends the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act to eliminate the annual fee on health insurance providers set to be imposed beginning on January 1, 2013.
